### Health check (optional)
GET {{baseUrl}}/

### 1) Login - JSON body (use this if /auth/login expects JSON)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{username}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 1b) Login - Form body (use this if /auth/login expects OAuth2 form)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username={{username}}&password={{password}}

### 2) Create campaign
POST {{baseUrl}}/campaigns/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test campaign from PyCharm",
  "description": "demo"
}

### 3) Get my campaigns
GET {{baseUrl}}/campaigns/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4) Create QR code
POST {{baseUrl}}/qrcodes/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "QR test from PyCharm",
  "campaign_id": 1,
  "destination_url": "https://example.com",
  "qr_type": "url",
  "design_config": {
    "color": "#000000",
    "logo": ""
  }
}
